                  A new inuention, and almost inuincible forme of fortification, against the furious battery of Artillarie.
                  IT hath béene the common vse in all fortifications héeretofore, to place the earth behind the walles of the Fortresse, and therof to make Bulwarks and Ramparts, but in the construction of this inuincible fortresse, against the infernall furie of Artillarie, it is necessary to vse a new inuention to fo
                        •…
